01:00:41.538 --> 01:00:44.042
It's your fault,
she doesn't love you.

01:00:44.126 --> 01:00:46.419
She doesn't love you.

01:00:46.502 --> 01:00:48.464
Stop it!

01:00:48.547 --> 01:00:49.757
Stop it, stop it!

01:00:54.430 --> 01:00:55.556
Stop it.

01:00:55.640 --> 01:00:58.142
With
love in your heart,

01:00:58.224 --> 01:00:59.977
