heart and a brave soul.

01:18:46.804 --> 01:18:51.768
He's great.

01:18:54.189 --> 01:18:55.232
And this...

01:18:57.859 --> 01:18:59.361
Is Nightinglar.

01:19:05.328 --> 01:19:08.955
